                "invention-title": [
                    "Integrated photovoltaic electro-oxidation device for treating micro-plastics in water and preparation method of integrated photovoltaic electro-oxidation device",
                    "一种集成光伏的电氧化处理水中微塑料装置及其制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to an integrated photovoltaic electrooxidation device for treating microplastics in water, which comprises an electrolysis device, and the electrolysis device comprises a cathode and an anode; the anode is integrated on the photovoltaic panel, the photovoltaic panel absorbs solar energy and converts the solar energy into electric energy, and the anode is integrated on the backlight side of the photovoltaic panel; the anode and the cathode are both in contact with sewage to be treated, after electrification, the micro-plastic is degraded into carbon dioxide and water at the anode, and the anode material is a TiO2 catalyst with Ti-site defects; the cathode material is a metal electrode, and dissolved oxygen in water at the cathode is converted into hydrogen peroxide. By efficiently combining a photovoltaic technology, a photo-thermal technology and an electro-oxidation technology, a photoelectric/photo-thermal-electro-oxidation treatment means is formed, the degradation efficiency of micro-plastics in water is remarkably improved, and the method has the characteristics of simplicity in operation, high efficiency, economy, greenness, low cost and the like."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种集成光伏的电氧化处理水中微塑料装置，包括电解装置，电解装置包括阴极和阳极；阳极集成在光伏板上，光伏板吸收太阳能转换为电能，阳极集成在光伏板背光侧；阳极和阴极均与待处理污水接触，通电后，微塑料在阳极处降解为二氧化碳和水，阳极材料为Ti位缺陷的TiO2催化剂；阴极材料为金属电极，在阴极处水中溶解氧转换为双氧水。本发明通过将光伏技术、光热技术和电氧化技术高效结合，形成光电/光热‑电氧化处理手段，显著提高水中微塑料的降解效率，具有操作简单、高效、经济绿色、成本低等特点。"
                }
            ]
        }
